om/2012/12/20/mac-game-of-the-week-borderlands-2-gets-exclusive-content-for-t/\">Borderlands 2 arrived on the Mac</a> late last year, but unfortunately the publisher, Aspyr Media, wasn't able to get the multiplayer working in time for the release. Today the company has <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id570316450?mt=12\">released a patch</a> that enables multiplayer co-op through Game Center, along with leaderboards and achievements.</p><p>
